If you don&#39;t want the content on disk, you could alternatively implement your own in-memory [`URLStreamHandler`][1], and specify it when creating the URL using the [`URL(String protocol, String host, int port, String file, URLStreamHandler handler)`][2] constructor. This is a lot more involved and beyond the scope of this answer.


